Dirty Shirley}{\cf1\dbch\af2\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f2
\~ : Dirty Shirley amp by Dave Friedman of Rack Systems,  classic rock amp (based on a JTM-45) designed to to be fat sounding. Speakers\~ : G12M, G12H. Stock cabs\~ : 36/37/38/58/60/61/96/101/102/103 (G12M), 16/34/57/64 (G12H).}
\par \pard\plain \s19\ql\sl276\slmult1\widctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\sb0\sa120\ltrpar\cf0\hich\af3\langfe2052\dbch\af4\afs22\lang1025\loch\f3\fs22\lang1036{\cf1\ul\ulc0\b\dbch\af2\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f2
Friedman BE / HBE}{\cf1\dbch\af2\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f2
\~ : Friedman Brown Eye / Hairy Brown Eye. BE\~ : Brown Eye, what many call }{\cf1\i\dbch\af2\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f2
\'ab\~ the ultimate modded Plexi\~ \'bb}{\cf1\dbch\af2\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f2
. HBE\~ : Hairy Brown Eye, the BE amp\'92s alternate voicing with a gain boost. Speakers\~ : G12M, G12H, V30. Stock cabs\~ : 16/34/57/64 (G12H)\~ ; 41/43/44/47/48/51/53/59/62/63/65/60/70/71/72/108 (V30)\~ ; 36/37/38/58/60/61/96/101/102/103 (G12M). Premier Guitar review\~ : }{\cf1\i\dbch\af2\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f2
\'ab\~ What really sets it apart is its Presence control. The knob doesn\'92t simply boost highs and add shimmer, it adds more girth, dimension, gain, and perceptible volume. Taming the Brown Eye\'92s high-gain settings only required lowering the Presence knob, which softened the high-end response and eased off the screaming gain a bit\~ \'bb}{\cf1\dbch\af2\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f2
. Cliff\~ : }{\cf1\i\dbch\af2\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f2
\'ab\~ The BE/HBE has a fixed depth circuit that gives a lot of bass boost. The model defaults the Depth to match this\~ \'bb}{\cf1\dbch\af2\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f2
.}
\par \pard\plain \s19\ql\sl276\slmult1\widctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\sb0\sa120\ltrpar\cf0\hich\af3\langfe2052\dbch\af4\afs22\lang1025\loch\f3\fs22\lang1036{\cf1\ul\ulc0\b\dbch\af2\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f2
FAS Crunch}{\cf1\dbch\af2\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f2
\~ : Custom Fractal model. Firmware 9\~ : }{\cf1\i\dbch\af2\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f2
\'ab\~ Our take on the ultimate British-sounding amp. More dynamic and open than a Plexi, but with more gain\~ \'bb}
\par \pard\plain \s19\ql\sl276\slmult1\widctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\sb0\sa120\ltrpar\cf0\hich\af3\langfe2052\dbch\af4\afs22\lang1025\loch\f3\fs22\lang1036{\cf1\ul\ulc0\b\dbch\af2\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f2
