\'ab\~ These are preamp models. Turn supply sag to something nonzero to engage a generic 6L6 power amp model (\'85) If you WANT to use the power amp modeling (which I would) turn the Supply Sag up to, say, 2.0 and then adjust the MV as described. I did not use a Boogie power amp model with these as I always preferred using my Triaxis with a more typical tube power amp \'bb}{\cf1\dbch\af2\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\loch\f2
.}
